---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/base-layout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Disclaimer" description="Important disclaimer regarding Srini.pro website content and course materials.">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Disclaimer</h1>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-gray-700">
      <section class="bg-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-yellow-400">
        <p class="font-semibold text-lg">Important: Please read this disclaimer carefully before using our website and courses.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Website Content Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>All website information is "published in good faith and for general information purpose only." The site makes no warranties regarding completeness, reliability, or accuracy of its content.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Use at Your Own Risk</h2>
        <p>Users access the site's information at their own risk; Srini.pro bears no liability for losses or damages resulting from website use.</p>
        <p class="mt-3">By accessing and using this website, you acknowledge and accept the risk that the information provided may contain inaccuracies or omissions.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Course Materials Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>The course materials and examples provided are for educational purposes only. Users should:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-3 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Test thoroughly:</strong> Always test code and procedures thoroughly before implementing in production environments</li>
          <li><strong>Verify accuracy:</strong> Verify that the methods taught are appropriate for your specific SAP environment and requirements</li>
          <li><strong>Seek expert guidance:</strong> Consult with SAP experts and your organization's IT team before implementing production changes</li>
          <li><strong>Backup systems:</strong> Maintain proper backups before testing any procedures on production systems</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">External Links Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>External hyperlinks are provided without guarantee. The site states: "we have no control over the content and nature of these sites" and such links don't imply endorsement of all content found there.</p>
        <p class="mt-3">Linked websites may have different privacy policies and terms of service beyond Srini.pro's control, and users should review these independently.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">No Employment Guarantee</h2>
        <p>The site emphasizes it does not guarantee employment outcomes and provides educational content only. Course completion does not guarantee employment, promotion, or career advancement.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">No Professional Advice</h2>
        <p>The content provided on Srini.pro is for educational and informational purposes only. It is not intended as professional advice, and you should not rely solely on this information for business, legal, or technical decisions.</p>
        <p class="mt-3">For professional advice specific to your situation, consult with qualified experts in your field.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>Srini.pro shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, including loss of profits, data, or business interruption, arising from:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-3 space-y-1">
          <li>Your use of or inability to use the website or courses</li>
          <li>Implementation of course materials in your systems</li>
          <li>Reliance on information provided on this site</li>
          <li>Any viruses, bugs, or errors in the website</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Consent to Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>By using the website, visitors consent to this disclaimer and agree to its terms.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Questions or Concerns?</h2>
        <p>For questions about this disclaimer or any concerns about the website or courses, please contact us at:</p>
        <p class="mt-3"><strong>Email: contact@srini.pro</strong></p>
      </section>

      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-12">Last Updated: June 23, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
